ta\";s:1575:\"<h3>New plugins</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/features-by-woothemes/\"><strong>Features by WooThemes</strong></a> is a clean and easy-to-use features showcase management system.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://blog.milandinic.com/wordpress/plugins/nav-menu-images/\"><strong>Nav Menu Images</strong></a> enables uploading of images for nav menu items on the menu edit screen.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/post-via-dropbox/\"><strong>Post via Dropbox</strong></a> allows you to post or edit your blog with text files uploaded via Dropbox.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/testimonials-by-woothemes/\"><strong>Testimonials by WooThemes</strong></a> is a clean and easy-to-use testimonials management system.</p>\n<h3>Updated plugins</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://ocaoimh.ie/exploit-scanner/\"><strong>Exploit Scanner</strong></a> searches the files on your website, and the posts and comments tables of your database for anything suspicious. It also examines your list of active plugins for unusual filenames.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://jetpack.me/\"><strong>Jetpack</strong></a> allows you to supercharge your WordPress site with powerful features previously only available to WordPress.com users.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/yet-another-related-posts-plugin/\"><strong>Yet Another Related Posts Plugin</strong></a> displays a list of related entries on your site and feeds based on a unique algorithm.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/WIGh0uTTkeI\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 26 Oct 2012 14:30:04 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4