lts, to take their physical limitations into account when training- if an exercise is unhealthy for you, don\'t do it. Students with unusually severe disabilities should make time with the instructor (in free-training sessions, or in private lessons) to work out ways to adapt the Art to their particular body.\r\nTraining at the school cannot replace medical supervision or physiotherapy. If you have any doubts, consult your doctor and the instructor before starting training.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<pre></pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>full calendar example</h3>\r\n[google-calendar-events id=\"1\" type=\"ajax\" title=\"Events on\" max=\"10\"]','Training','','inherit','open','open','','19-revision-28','','','2012-09-27 18:42:03','2012-09-27 16:42:03','',19,'http://swordschool.axis-of-evil.org/?p=94',0,'revision','',0),(95,1,'2012-09-17 21:05:09','2012-09-17 19:05:09','Book an Event content','Book an Event','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-3','','','2012-09-17 21:05:09','2012-09-17 19:05:09','',17,'http://swordschool.axis-of-evil.org/?p=95',0,'revision','',0),(96,1,'2012-10-02 18:24:47','2012-10-02 16:24:47','Book an Event content','Book an Event','','inherit','open','open','','17-autosave','','','2012-10-02 18:24:47','2012-10-02 16:24:47','',17,'http://swordschool.axis-of-evil.org/?p=96',0,'revision','',0),(97,1,'2012-10-02 18:16:41','2012-10-02 16:16:41','Book an Event content','Book an Event','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-4','','','2012-10-02 18:16:41','2012-10-02 16:16:41','',17,'http://swordschool.axis-of-evil.org/?p=97',0,'revision','',0),(98,1,'2012-10-02 18:18:01','2012-10-02 16:18:01','Book an Event content','Book an Event','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-5','','','2012-10-02 18:18:01','2012-10-02 16:18:01','',17,'http://swordschool.axis-of-evil.org/?p=98',0,'revision','',0),(99,1,'2012-10-02 18:18:16','2012-10-02 16:18:16','Book an Event content','Book an Event','','inherit','open','open','','17-revision-6','','','2012-10-02 18:18:16','2012-